    "endTime": 5.505000000000001,
    "text": "I can hear that beast."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.572,
    "endTime": 6.773,
    "text": "- Yeah. - Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.84,
    "endTime": 7.574,
    "text": "Loud and clear."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.11,
    "endTime": 15.382,
    "text": "I've been fishing in some remote places, but never in front of an audience of hippos."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.448,
    "endTime": 18.017,
    "text": "I'm constantly looking over, because those things charge."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.084,
    "endTime": 19.652,
    "text": "Lonely."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.719,
    "endTime": 20.487000000000002,
    "text": "Yes?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.553,
    "endTime": 22.322,
    "text": "That thing's getting closer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.389,
    "endTime": 23.622,
    "text": "Yes, I can see it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.69,
    "endTime": 24.424,
    "text": "We are safe for now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.491,
    "endTime": 25.558,
    "text": "Are you sure?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.625,
    "endTime": 26.393,
    "text": "Yes, yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.0,
    "endTime": 28.0,
    "text": "I'll tell you when to run."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.495,
    "endTime": 30.330000000000002,
    "text": "Lonely, I'm three times heavier than you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.397,
    "endTime": 31.564,
    "text": "I don't move that quickly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.631,
    "endTime": 32.499,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.564,
    "endTime": 34.166,
    "text": "I can see they run faster than you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.234,
    "endTime": 35.602000000000004,
    "text": "Trust me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.668,
    "endTime": 37.57,
    "text": "I am not leaving here until I catch a decent fish."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.637,
    "endTime": 38.972,
    "text": "Yes, yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.038,
    "endTime": 40.272,
    "text": "Come on, bass."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.34,
    "endTime": 42.542,
    "text": "I'd like to catch a f****ing fish."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.609,
    "endTime": 44.577,
    "text": "Come on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.644,
    "endTime": 45.412,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.478,
    "endTime": 46.246,
    "text": "I think I've got one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.312,
    "endTime": 47.814,
    "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.881,
    "endTime": 49.082,
    "text": "No. No I haven't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.149,
    "endTime": 50.183,
    "text": "- You missed it. - No, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.25,
    "endTime": 51.351,
    "text": "- He's on. - Still on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.418,
    "endTime": 52.318,
    "text": "He's still on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.385,
    "endTime": 53.352,
    "text": "Yes, yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.42,
    "endTime": 55.722,
    "text": "Pull it back slowly, slowly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.789,
    "endTime": 56.79,
    "text": "Good. Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.856,
    "endTime": 57.624,
    "text": "Good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.69,
    "endTime": 59.692,
    "text": "You see?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.759,
    "endTime": 61.861,
    "text": "Now that is a good one for the..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.928,
    "endTime": 63.062,
    "text": "- For the chief. - For the chief right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.07,
    "endTime": 65.5532,
    "text": "He's going to be happy, eh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.532,
    "endTime": 71.271,
    "text": "Now Lonely may have caught the most fish, but let's be honest, I caught the biggest."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.337,
    "endTime": 73.57300000000001,
    "text": "I want to save my fish for the chief."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.64,
    "endTime": 76.242,
    "text": "So I'm taking one of Lonely's back to Zola."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.309,
    "endTime": 77.844,
    "text": "She might assume that I caught it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.911,
    "endTime": 80.88,
    "text": "But if you don't say anything, I won't either."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.947,
    "endTime": 81.714,
    "text": "Zola."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.781,
    "endTime": 83.016,
    "text": "Hey!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.082,
    "endTime": 84.28299999999999,
    "text": "We are not empty-handed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.35,
    "endTime": 85.785,
    "text": "Oh, look at that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.852,
    "endTime": 87.921,
    "text": "I'd like you to scale and gut that guy for me, please."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.987,
    "endTime": 89.155,
    "text": "Scale and gut it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.222,
    "endTime": 93.226,
    "text": "The point here for the week is to hone your Zulu warriors skills."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.293,
    "endTime": 94.427,
    "text": "Right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.494,
    "endTime": 96.463,
    "text": "Braaing is quintessential."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.529,
    "endTime": 99.899,
    "text": "We're keeping it very plain, very simple, just a little bit of seasoning."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.966,
    "endTime": 101.768,
    "text": "The ingredients speak for themselves, generally."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.835,
    "endTime": 103.002,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.069,
    "endTime": 107.10600000000001,
    "text": "Which is, you know, in line with tradition, in terms of our flavor profile of Zulu people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.173,
    "endTime": 108.47500000000001,
    "text": "Gotcha."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.541,
    "endTime": 112.11,
    "text": "So here I'm making something called ushatini."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.178,
    "endTime": 117.14999999999999,
    "text": "It's a combination of onions and tomatoes, chopped up, which I've got here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.217,
    "endTime": 120.0,
    "text": "And I've been mentioning to you how, you know, the Zulu palate is very simplistic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 122.121,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.188,
    "endTime": 127.36,
    "text": "But KZN is the biggest population of Indian people outside of India."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.427,
    "endTime": 129.996,
    "text": "We do add a touch of chili every now and then."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.062,
    "endTime": 131.33100000000002,
    "text": "Right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.397,
    "endTime": 134.868,
    "text": "Because that sort of culture has infiltrated throughout the region."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.934,
    "endTime": 136.102,
    "text": "So no oil?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.169,
    "endTime": 136.97,
    "text": "No oil."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.036,
    "endTime": 138.238,
    "text": "No, no oil."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.304,
    "endTime": 139.806,
    "text": "Remember, this is Zulu warrior cooking."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.873,
    "endTime": 141.374,
    "text": "Sure."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.441,
    "endTime": 143.309,
    "text": "There was no such thing as olive oil available, et cetera."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.376,
    "endTime": 145.144,
    "text": "So you just went straight on to the fire."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.211,
    "endTime": 147.58,
    "text": "- Straight on? - On to the fire, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.647,
    "endTime": 148.67999999999998,
    "text": "So wherever you see the coals at their whitest you'll know that they're the right temperature. - There."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.251,
    "endTime": 152.018,
    "text": "There you go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.085,
    "endTime": 153.786,
    "text": "Good sizzle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.853,
    "endTime": 155.288,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.355,
    "endTime": 156.756,
    "text": "What's becoming very obvious is that it's very simple."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.823,
    "endTime": 158.324,
    "text": "That's it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.391,
    "endTime": 162.161,
    "text": "This tribal cooking, in a way that it's a huge emphasis on the fish and the meat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.228,
    "endTime": 163.363,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.429,
    "endTime": 164.964,
    "text": "What's the big no-nos for the chief?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.031,
    "endTime": 168.90200000000002,
    "text": "Zulu people in general do not like their meat rare."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.968,
    "endTime": 170.203,
    "text": "- I know - Damn."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.27,
    "endTime": 173.37300000000002,
    "text": "- You know, you're Gordon, so you're going to want to give them medium rare. - Damn."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.439,
    "endTime": 175.84099999999998,
    "text": "What would happen if you just try and suggest he takes it medium rare?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.909,
    "endTime": 177.44199999999998,
    "text": "I don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.51,
    "endTime": 180.0,
    "text": "I've never heard anyone suggest anything to the chief before."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.0,
    "endTime": 182.248,
    "text": "But you could be the first, Gordon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.315,
    "endTime": 183.55,
    "text": "Beautiful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.616,
    "endTime": 185.21800000000002,
    "text": "Beautiful, fresh piece of fish."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.285,
    "endTime": 186.452,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.519,
    "endTime": 187.58700000000002,
    "text": "- Right on there. - Oh my god."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.654,
    "endTime": 189.355,
    "text": "Hang onto that for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.422,
    "endTime": 192.058,
    "text": "And then I'm going to pop the shatini on top of the flesh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.125,
    "endTime": 193.326,
    "text": "Amazing how simple it is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.393,
    "endTime": 199.631,
    "text": "And you think of the fierce warrior, in terms of what he stands for, how important he is, and look how simple that is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.699,
    "endTime": 200.43300000000002,
    "text": "That's it, simple."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.87,
    "endTime": 205.138,
    "text": "Delicious."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.204,
    "endTime": 206.306,
    "text": "- Good fishing. - That's delicious."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.372,
    "endTime": 207.507,
    "text": "Hmm. So good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.574,
    "endTime": 209.008,
    "text": "- So good. - But so simple."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.075,
    "endTime": 210.343,
    "text": "So simple."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.41,
    "endTime": 212.712,
    "text": "All the ingredients speak for themselves."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.779,
    "endTime": 214.647,
    "text": "I will see you, I'll see at the end of the week."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.714,
    "endTime": 215.515,
    "text": "At the end of the week."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.582,
    "endTime": 216.715,
    "text": "Any tips?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.783,
    "endTime": 219.819,
    "text": "-Mostly listen and learn. -Right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.886,
    "endTime": 223.0,
    "text": "And always remember, the chief is a hard man to please."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.0,
